tion", :text=>"And Noe was six hundred years old when the flood of water was upon the earth."}, {:version=>"Douay-Rheims Bible", :text=>"And he was six hundred years old, when the waters of the flood overflowed the earth. "}, {:version=>"Darby Bible Translation", :text=>"And Noah was six hundred years old when the flood of waters was on the earth."}, {:version=>"English Revised Version", :text=>"And Noah was six hundred years old when the flood of waters was upon the earth."}, {:version=>"Webster's Bible Translation", :text=>"And Noah was six hundred years old when the flood of waters was on the earth."}, {:version=>"World English Bible", :text=>"Noah was six hundred years old when the flood of waters came on the earth."}, {:version=>"Young's Literal Translation", :text=>" and Noah is a son of six hundred years, and the deluge of waters hath been upon the earth."}]}